        "title": "Ribonuclease L mediates the cell-lethal phenotype of the double-stranded RNA editing enzyme ADAR1 in a human cell line", 
        "published": "2017-03-31T00:00:00Z", 
        "versionDate": "2017-03-31T00:00:00Z", 
        "volume": 6, 
